trans-unit.source: Represents a symbol binder for managed code.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en symbolet dokumentordner for forvaltet kode.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir ressursene som brukes av den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Called by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Dispose*> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Finalize*> methods to release the managed and unmanaged resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av den <> </> *> og <> </> *> metoder for å frigjøre behandlet ressursene som brukes i den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder"> </xref> klassen.

trans-unit.source: This method is called only by the public <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Dispose%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Finalize%2A> methods; do not call this method directly.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles bare av offentlig <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Dispose%2A>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Finalize%2A>metoder; ikke kalle denne metoden direkte.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre ressurser behandlet. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources held by the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Frigir ressursene som gjeldende forekomst.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Application code should not call this method; an object's `Finalize` method is automatically invoked during garbage collection, unless finalization by the garbage collector has been disabled by a call to the <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Applikasjons-koden kan ikke kalle denne metoden. et objekts `Finalize` metode startes automatisk under datasanering, med mindre finalization av saneringsoppsamlingen er deaktivert av et kall til den <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A>metoden.</xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the interface of the symbol reader for the current file, using the specified 32-bit integer pointer to a metadata interface, the specified file name, and the specified search path.
trans-unit.target: Henter grensesnittet for symbolet leseren for den gjeldende filen ved hjelp av angitte 32-biters heltall pekeren til et grensesnitt for metadata, angitt filnavn og den angitte banen.

trans-unit.source: When given a pointer to a metadata interface, a file name, and a search path, the GetReader method returns the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader> interface that reads the debugging symbols associated with the module.
trans-unit.target: Når gitt en peker til et grensesnitt for metadata, et navn og en søkebane, GetReader returneres av <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader>grensesnitt som leser feilsøking symbolene som er forbundet med modulen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Using a 32-bit integer as a pointer is not recommended.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Bruker en 32-biters heltall som en peker ikke anbefales.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.GetReader%2A> overload instead.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.GetReader%2A>overbelaste i stedet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.SymBinder.GetReader%2A>

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit integer that points to the metadata import interface.
trans-unit.target: Et 32-biters heltall som peker til grensesnittet metadata import.

trans-unit.source: The name of the file for which the reader interface is required.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på filen grensesnittet leseren kreves.

trans-unit.source: The search path used to locate the symbol file.
trans-unit.target: Søkebanen som ble brukt til å finne filen symbolet.

trans-unit.source: The interface that reads the debugging symbols.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet som leser feilsøking symboler.
